+When multiple `ContainerExecutionCondition` or `TestExecutionCondition` extensions are registered,
+a container or test, respectively, is skipped as soon as one of them returns _skipped_. Thus, there
+is no guarantee that a condition extension is called because another extension might already caused
+a container or test to be skipped. In other words, the evaluation works like the short-circuiting
+boolean OR operator.
